Outpatient cost parameters

Source: R/data.R
params_costs_op.Rd

Mean monthly outpatient costs by health state.

params_costs_op

Format

A data table with the following columns:

state_name

Name of the health state.

mean

Mean outpatient costs.

se

Standard error of outpatient costs.

ref

BibTeX reference for estimate.

Examples

print(params_costs_op)
#>    state_name mean  se                   ref
#> 1:         S1   63  15      graham2018budget
#> 2:      P1/S2 1624 170 skinner2018healthcare
#> 3:         P2 1287 134 skinner2018healthcare
